{"tid":1168910,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[初遊記]十一日大阪，東京","createTime":"2019-05-24T04:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T04:18:28.000Z","uid":187973,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f282db1c4e6896fbaa6f2092c81873d737b8746c","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"一直想寫遊記但成日都唔記得影相，見今次有d相po下咁所以開個po。相唔係好齊希望大家見諒下，下次會齊好多。<br />\n<br />\n話說前排mid-sem就去左日本一轉，後半撞正黃金週所以東京都好多唔同fes去。唔講咁多睇相先。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 1</span></span><br />\n朝早就係SYD出發坐QF去關空<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KV1Aodp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKV1Aodp.jpg&h=e72932e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bksWR6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbksWR6M.jpg&h=81343913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個lounge幾寬敞幾舒服<br />\n不過野食選擇有d少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7gTUkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7gTUkY.jpg&h=e6755888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFkdUk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFkdUk8.jpg&h=28b901b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛大阪係用A330<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過就用新款J唔洗隔離有人坐，又有張床單仔咁<br />\n<br />\n由於太眼訓快手食左個lunch就訓左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0em3fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0em3fe.jpg&h=5aedb51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApproach前一個鐘有light refreshment,  個名係唔知乜soba, hmmm&hellip;"},{"pid":"d3038fac0ebc813ba81ef2d599e4740d7f055056","tid":1168910,"uid":94548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"獨遊？"},{"pid":"9d0494e4c3ac4fa7412992df6ae4caddb061e1b2","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3038fac0ebc813ba81ef2d599e4740d7f055056","tid":1168910,"uid":94548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"獨遊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"一半一半，d朋友全部係日本所以每日都見唔同人"},{"pid":"6cab1adb20875d17f0102649909f7e3c5927e416","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"落機就去左心斎橋間串炸店食左個course<br />\n有三個前菜，沙律，煮牛肉，本日煸炒（唔識譯&hellip;）<br />\n每人12款串炸同2個鐘任飲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5RHNNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5RHNNr.jpg&h=2ba29cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n掛住飲冇乜影相，可以去tabelog睇睇，有成3.58分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/osaka/A2701/A270201/27050413/top_amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Fosaka%2FA2701%2FA270201%2F27050413%2Ftop_amp%2F&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=eeb79582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/osaka/A2701/A270201/27050413/top_amp/</a><br />\n不過記憶中係冇英文menu<br />\n<br />\n酒店就住新大阪APA Hotel。房相就冇，不過就唔少得佢地嘅生招牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGT3xfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGT3xfB.jpg&h=33b7a34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網book幾多晚就送返咁多盒社長咖哩比你，我真係多謝你啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018374b8e6bd2462429d25714e39d5f0d6ccb85f","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 2</span></span><br />\n第二日就去左搭一日兩班新開由新大阪出發，大阪東線嘅直通快速去奈良。第一次去覺得幾有風味不過真係大多觀光客好迫，冇乜事都唔會再去觀光景點&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJOfoyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJOfoyv.jpg&h=008ec14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RMMD5MS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRMMD5MS.jpg&h=db89cf47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UsseFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UsseFd.jpg&h=0992871b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFHLLMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFHLLMW.jpg&h=6b8b9b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3OfoDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3OfoDA.jpg&h=f3e9bd1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWWQcrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWWQcrX.jpg&h=f6ebc4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7BmXBTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BmXBTE.jpg&h=e67824a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好彩仲有一棵櫻花未謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見有間炖牛筋咖哩幾好食咁冇起底就坐低左，但係你要加錢先有肉食，basic就得肉絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qb7Dmom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQb7Dmom.jpg&h=6b18301f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://r.gnavi.co.jp/k742121/?utm_id=sales-sem-pr_izky_osaka_cosmic_sp_g_lis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.gnavi.co.jp%2Fk742121%2F%3Futm_id%3Dsales-sem-pr_izky_osaka_cosmic_sp_g_lis&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=fa9dcf5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.gnavi.co.jp/k742121/?utm_id=sales-sem-pr_izky_osaka_cosmic_sp_g_lis</a><br />\n夜晚去左間柚子料理專門居酒屋，3000円2個鐘任食任飲+500再多一個鐘<br />\n又係掛住飲所以冇相睇sorry&hellip;"},{"pid":"86f357126dad8e0e3e3dbf76f7359a692fb5d787","tid":1168910,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"行程？"},{"pid":"466599535e54e9f8120af186f770afc2a59e2753","tid":1168910,"uid":138996,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"用特區，俾負皮先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nanyway 樓主繼續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a23a696009f589489c901bd67523007df6290a3","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打提醒，補返個行程先<br />\n<br />\nDay 1:到關西機場；checkin新大阪站南APA酒店；串炸專門店 心斎橋カラッと<br />\n<br />\nDay 2:奈良半日遊，和牛筋咖哩；柚子小町 難波本店<br />\n<br />\nDay 3: 拉麵 死老野嘅最後一擊，十三；睇柯南；sushi tetsu 先斗町<br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 鯛白湯拉麵 ○de▽，新大阪；半日Round1 Spocha，高規；京都焼鳥製作所，bar moon walk木屋町<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: 人類大家都係麵類；新幹線&rarr;東京，check-in 東横イン池袋北口 2；北戸田鳥貴族<br />\n<br />\nDay 6: 藤浪；江之島半日遊；秋葉原魚金<br />\n<br />\nDay 7: 拉麵 鬼金棒，池袋東口；梅酒祭，上野；啤酒吧 STAND1，新丸之內大廈；   居酒屋 金八，八重洲<br />\n<br />\nDay 8: 國營日立海濱公園半日遊；立ち飲み屋 秋葉酒場，隠れ家bar cafe&amp;bar luxe；check in APA酒店秋葉原電氣街口<br />\n<br />\nDay 9: Hea行秋葉原；池袋大酒場<br />\n<br />\nDay 10: Cafe Pinocchio，大山；cafe 手紙舎，杜鵑丘；翻兜秋葉原魚金<br />\n<br />\nDay 11: 拉麵 Afuri，六本木；布甸祭/肉祭，台場"},{"pid":"c6e19979414525a65247d530becabe4dd4c4cc93","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 3</span></span><br />\nBrunch去左酒店附近十三站有間拉麵叫「死老野嘅最後一擊」，湯底係蜆base豉油味。平時都排好長不過今日排左4個就有得入去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcfYnLj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcfYnLj.jpg&h=80ea8509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯頭有三種，淡、中、濃，分別配細、中、大size嘅蜆。仲加左個蜆飯同蜆餃子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/504m4Zw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F504m4Zw.jpg&h=d12cd449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紺青之拳，有基德一定好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EibwHMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEibwHMv.jpg&h=c23d7306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜晚就去左間係三条即叫即整嘅寿司鋪，而每客兩件都係100円！係100円！！又多選擇又新鮮，所以成日都要排隊，建議book定位先。"},{"pid":"0534e690c32449af327d0f8c203b2ec42bd7c9ba","tid":1168910,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"e4ccc0940fe3edee557cc27e386f3a4cf52909a2","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 4</span></span><br />\n繼續係用拉麵迎接新一天，呢日就去左新大阪站另一邊食，間野叫做「鯛白湯拉麵○de▽」，顧名思義就係個湯底係用鯛魚淆出泥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5inWY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5inWY9.jpg&h=a3336f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係個兩款，濃厚同清爽。自己比較鐘意個味重d所以就叫左濃厚，想飲湯就叫清爽。夜晚就會有多個沾麵簡不過限定30個手快有手慢冇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JK92W05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJK92W05.jpg&h=dd264908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n濃厚（とろり）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/To7HczE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTo7HczE.jpg&h=7080e2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清爽（さらり）<br />\n<br />\n鐘意魚介類湯底嘅巴絲打一定要去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775fc1cb8437ce3a8292f35694dc13ce0d7ad965","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"夜晚去左京都食燒鳥，呢間係我每次去京都一定要食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgC0J0o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgC0J0o.jpg&h=c3bffe5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2e2Xkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2e2Xkq.jpg&h=45cbe842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GX2zOr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGX2zOr6.jpg&h=349a429d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ns1XMdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNs1XMdO.jpg&h=0f25cc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇落好似冇乜特別係因為我影相廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就一如以往去飲野，去左一間cocktail吧，原因係全部cocktail均一200円！而且佢亦係電影<span style=\"color: blue;\">「春宵苦短，少女前進吧！」</span>嘅舞台之一，所以順便朝拜下聖地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnCgheE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfnCgheE.jpg&h=5e1f0cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">偽電気ブラン</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 5</span></span><br />\n由於第五日係移動同hea main，而大家都應該好熟悉鳥貴族所以唔多講。不過當然冇比個拉麵修行停，今次繼續係魚介類「人類みな麺類」，係新大阪搭御堂筋線一個站去到西中島南方行一陣就到，開門前20分鐘到都已經排哂隊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5LfhMcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5LfhMcw.jpg&h=d8bba13c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e31bf8c5157ecd66f623260f9308d89f82933abd","tid":1168910,"uid":187973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 6</span></span><br />\n由於要去江之島所以被迫停止我個一日一拉麵修行。講到江之島就緊係要帶個朋友去食白飯魚啦，只不過太肚餓之餘出名個間又要排好耐就求其搵間食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1bs8wy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1bs8wy.jpg&h=f95c94a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2色丼: 釜揚げしらす、真鯛</span><br />\n<br />\n江之島嘅遊記應周街都執到幾個所以po幾張就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLamtye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLamtye.jpg&h=94ab8865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOTvmTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOTvmTf.jpg&h=a0e0d145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpgkJ6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrpgkJ6v.jpg&h=75f89d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkYOSZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkYOSZR.jpg&h=5a6d6dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbJy36y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbJy36y.jpg&h=9fd4746c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3Vmtyg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3Vmtyg.jpg&h=b04b350c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kr8SAdi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkr8SAdi.jpg&h=00d935aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">ps 如果個日冇船搭返出去，有條shortcut落島快好多！係賣羊羹間野之前左轉就得</span>"},{"pid":"4c99da647389d6c6ee319de3160d8c3488396afb","tid":1168910,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:42:36.000Z","msg":"留"},{"pid":"716a1122c88dc7dca572ae4d24bf70fd8ef59e8e","tid":1168910,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e7d26f433633584890d75c37bbc0575cf00490cf","tid":1168910,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"留名，嚟緊7 月8月會去"},{"pid":"7a0b51e204156137d00f92ef5daf440600ed3ecb","tid":1168910,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"推下<br />\n想睇江之島同日立公園"},{"pid":"44c1f54db1f7273bf8264be670c5ac05076d6e70","tid":1168910,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:17:31.000Z","msg":"我又係勁中意食拉麵<br />\n<br />\n近來去日本就一日一沾麵"},{"pid":"49b3ed6f0200bb715b8e891b25740f10d7f3143b","tid":1168910,"uid":222787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae039a9fb786537d60a6d8c69d69c